What you need to know:  This is a valley of death, where human life is cheaper than that of a goat. It is a home of scared people losing the zest of longevity; it is a magnet for bandits.The sheer disregard for the law is shocking. Where the bandits get the guns is not a mystery, and they have some of the best weapons and ammunition.Cattle raids–often fuelled by retrogressive cultural practices–are common. The veneer of civilisation is fragile.